rows.label: qst105702_msg0002
rows.name:
Zadazan never expect friends
chase all the way here.

rows.label: qst105702_msg0021
rows.name:
Oh? Friends surprised to see
Zadazan here?

rows.label: qst105702_msg0022
rows.name:
Mo-mo-mo. Friends come in search
of Bahn-sama's money, yes?

rows.label: qst105702_msg0023
rows.name:
Members of Lindwurm concealed
in all places. We always watching.

rows.label: qst105702_msg0051
rows.name:
And you, friends...
You no more than nuisance to
great plans of Lindwurm.

rows.label: qst105702_msg0052
rows.name:
Facing Zadazan is most foolish move
of friends. You end here today!

rows.label: qst105702_msg0008
rows.name:
Mo-mo! Before me reduce friends to
ash, Zadazan tell you little secret.

rows.label: qst105702_msg0071
rows.name:
Money of Bahn-sama go towards
realization of ultimate Lindwurm goal...

rows.label: qst105702_msg0073
rows.name:
The more prosperous Avaritia Guild
become, the closer Empire draw to
destruction.

rows.label: qst105702_msg0013
rows.name:
Now friends have honor of testing
new military might we obtain using
money of Bahn-sama!
